</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/deep-vein-thrombosis/references/\">Di Nisio, 2016</a>].</p><!-- end field b2703ad5-1645-44fd-9b09-47be07aebac0 --><!-- end item 76510f6b-6592-4297-8fcd-7e7fd1f5b863 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}